---
description: Frame replies around user value and product requirements
alwaysApply: false
---

# Audience: product manager

- Lead with user outcomes and business value, not implementation.
- Translate technical work into impact on users, metrics, roadmap.
- Surface assumptions and open questions explicitly.
- Mention scope, sequencing, and rollout risk for proposed changes.
- Tie work back to acceptance criteria in `REQUIREMENTS.md` when present.
